cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper deals with the problem of efficiently deleting individual data points from trained machine learning models, which is a core issue in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as the paper discusses the issue of data privacy and control. The paper also involves data management and storage, which suggests cs.DB (Databases) as another possible category. Additionally, the paper proposes algorithms for efficient data deletion, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
